data.description: BETTER THAN NEW! This one story home in popular Autumn Lakes offers 22 solar panels that were installed in 2022 offering a remarkably low summer electric bill of only $17/mo. Tucked at the end of a long cul de sac it is situated on a level lot that backs up to a natural area! Enjoy entertaining in the backyard with patio, fire pit and 6 foot privacy fence! This home lives large with a functional floorplan and vaulted ceilings! Slab construction so NO stairs.  Only 5 minutes to shopping, dining and hwy 87 for quick access to Raleigh! Refrigerator and security cameras convey. Awesome neighborhood playground and dog park. Wake County Schools. NO DOWNPAYMENT USDA ELIGIBLE FINANCING!
